name.k: Brothers: A Tale of Two Sons

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Two heads are better than one

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Sent on an epic quest to save their father, two siblings must work together to complete a stunning and obstacle-ridden journey. As you make your way across vast landscapes, you’ll discover a world subtly tinged with sorrow and tenderness. Brothers’ unique control scheme puts you in command of both characters at once, and solving the puzzles requires coordination and consideration. While working out the problems is rewarding—and occasionally thought-provoking—it’s the unique way the gameplay and tone mesh together that’ll stick with you.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Guide two siblings on an epic, moving voyage through the wilderness.
兄と弟、二人の力を合わせてお父さんを救い出す壮大な旅に出かけよう。
